name: Bweye
description:
My gift to the first 15 collectors of 'The Eye'.
Thank you very much!

Bweye uses the same algorithm as 'The Eye', with a few parameters changed.
The animation restarts on every page load / resize screen / click on canvas / press SPACE.

This is the 2nd in a series of 3 pieces, each with an edition size of 15 (the first one was burned down from 25 to 15).

912 bytes of pure JavaScript
